INSERT INTO public.quotations VALUES (538, 'GE₆ 20 ina ZALAG₂ sin ina IGI MAŠ.MAŠ IGI 2 KUŠ₃ sin 5 1/2 KUŠ₃ ana ULU₃ SIG', '', 273, 'Night of (day) 20, last part of the night, Sin was 2 cubits in front of the front twin, Sin being 5 1/2 cubits low to the south.', 'BM 32839+ (ADRT III No. -141F)', 'astronomical diary', 'Babylon', '142 BCE', 'Sachs, A. J., Hunger, H. 1996. Astronomical Diaries and Related Texts from Babylonia, Vol. III. Diaries from 164 B.C. to 61 B.C. Vienna, Austria: Verlag der Österreichischen Akademie der Wissenschaften.', '', 'obv. 5''', 372, '124-125', '');
